    "Html": "<p>I've got this, which I see other people say should inherit styles, bottom line is it's not.&nbsp; I'm applying the theme with:</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:medium\">\r\n<p>Windows.Application.Current.Resources = XamlReader.Load(xml.CreateReader())</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>If that makes any difference.&nbsp; XML is an XElement with the theme in it.&nbsp; I happen to be pulling from a resource.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">StackPanel</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Orientation</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;Horizontal&quot;&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">StackPanel.Resources</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">Style</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> BasedOn</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;{</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">StaticResource</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"> {</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">x</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">:</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">Type</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Button</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">}}&quot;</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> TargetType</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;Button&quot;&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">Setter</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Property</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;Width&quot;</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;80&quot;/&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">Setter</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Property</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;Margin&quot;</span></span><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000;font-size:medium\"> Value</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">=&quot;0,0,8,0&quot;/&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">Style</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">StackPanel.Resources</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&gt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><br></span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;font-size:medium\">&nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\"><span style=\"color:#a31515;font-size:medium\">